{"tid":82483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當年加租逾倍逼走添好運　業主今蝕850萬賣舖","createTime":"2017-01-16T03:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T03:51:07.000Z","uid":34005,"like":394,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0fb85cd325445e84ca097f6b60de227bc9cc37d","tid":82483,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tim-13_esGJ9_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftim-13_esGJ9_1200x0.png&h=d8edcf83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》報道，旺角廣華街一個街舖以3,346.8萬售出，較業主2012年購入時貶值逾600萬，連使費料蝕超過850萬元。該舖位曾為米芝蓮食肆「添好運點心專門店」本店，2012新業主大幅加租逾倍，將添好運逼走。<br />\n<br />\n由四季飯店龍景軒點心師傅麥桂培創辦的點心舖「添好運點心專門店」，2009年在廣華街2-20號翠園大樓2期地下7號舖開張，舖位只能容納29個座位。添好運未幾即取得米芝蓮一星推薦，門庭若市大排長龍，吸引買家於2012年10月購入該舖，並向添好運大幅加租，由4.2萬加至11萬，令添好運決定搬舖。<br />\n<br />\n該業主於2012年10月，以4000萬購入該舖，日前以3346.8萬賣出，賬面蝕653.2萬，貶值16.3%，加上使費，整體虧蝕料達850萬。<br />\n<br />\n由四季飯店龍景軒點心師傅麥桂培創辦的點心舖「添好運點心專門店」，於2009年首獲評為米芝蓮一星食店，令該店升價十倍，日日排長龍，目前在香港已有數間分店，並打入新加坡、菲律賓、印尼、澳洲等亞太地區國家的市場，今秋會於美國紐約東村區開店。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%A0%E7%A7%9F%E9%80%BE%E5%80%8D%E9%80%BC%E8%B5%B0%E6%B7%BB%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8B-%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%8A%E8%9D%95850%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%A3%E8%88%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25A7%259F%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%2580%258D%25E9%2580%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E9%2581%258B-%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25BB%258A%25E8%259D%2595850%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E8%2588%2596%2F&d=zY%2FQSSMQZOo%2Fp9VqewScKmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=21fbb3b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%25A7%259F%25E9%2580%25BE%25E5%2580%258D%25E9%2580%25BC%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E9%2581%258B-%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25BB%258A%25E8%259D%2595850%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E8%2588%2596%2F&h=df9807a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E5%8A%A0%E7%A7%9F%E9%80%BE%E5%80%8D%E9%80%BC%E8%B5%B0%E6%B7%BB%E5%A5%BD%E9%81%8B-%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%8A%E8%9D%95850%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%A3%E8%88%96/</a>"},{"pid":"0d7906410fb223b4aeef3bb7325a78df4b3d4906","tid":82483,"uid":2087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3f0caae98dd3f1017b752b2956dbe9e6c6972d","tid":82483,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"你班炒家仲唔仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bddcb4e047f793f62752ffededf1f0a56400727","tid":82483,"uid":40422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54383d2c86816437acacb18e48cb197915f5498","tid":82483,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:47:27.000Z","msg":"殺雞取卵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c199d30a4d45a126fe021ddf78a88af99a5135c1","tid":82483,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:48:50.000Z","msg":"真係講句抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾華人社會 有得賺都唔夠 係要死加爛加煲到盡<br />\n破產跳樓死都唔會有人可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e964893d71952f54c7a4e035c0e2dc8f2e8240d","tid":82483,"uid":64385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:51:13.000Z","msg":"睇人仆街最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e1b98c0f5ae34d57bef6f05c29f178b