:0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e09d33b367a45e5ba442a90bef16768700109c9","tid":82483,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n華人老細就係咁短視</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  華人社會先有呢種賺埋你果份，最好我賺晒嘅心態</blockquote><br />\n華人劣質基因....加埋短視，呢刻賺到盡，跟住要倒蝕都唔撚理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n經濟下跌時，佢地通常唔肯接受大環境經濟變差，要個租客見到市面有大把吉舖選擇，要個租客有離意，佢一時又搵唔到人承租，冇人租一排，先死死地氣接受現實減租，睇見就肉酸，仲以為個勢嚮自己度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab622a846c0529189f5b0389bf74a3b48bce04f","tid":82483,"uid":33528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:37:27.000Z","msg":"其實呢<br />\n間嘢唔算特別好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申食過一次"},{"pid":"3bee06defc85099d22588f1cf90b1c62702eb833","tid":82483,"uid":71376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:38:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明鋪位車位呢啲冇辣招先最好炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鋪位同車位係直接Apply DSD<br />\n現時為劃一15%#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f30ea1c6a921095d1d2b9bb01c7fa3cf390294","tid":82483,"uid":34547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:40:51.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a784ae195c82252fc80f093846807381abc017fb","tid":82483,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T05:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71eef346d9ce0f0aec8540a744cb00a1cd45cb38","tid":82483,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":