d":82483,"uid":49318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:53:46.000Z","msg":"宜家有冇人租ga?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc5929046ea9fc688954a7c9c7a14f68346d2c2","tid":82483,"uid":41967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:56:24.000Z","msg":"四個字 抵撚死"},{"pid":"e2b032cda88c05fa3678e713d02e30b637e2f90f","tid":82483,"uid":24015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:58:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>租約先四萬，夠膽死用4000萬買間鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要放租83.3年先回本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淨係計年回報就知死啦，1%多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢加到11萬都只係3%回報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4312b9148bdec93f0d7c3db45959dd5963e6e803","tid":82483,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明鋪位車位呢啲冇辣招先最好炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鋪位郁下就8,9位數,點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781f86fba305a2f8ac0aeb27f3a0904f63a1e9a8","tid":82483,"uid":22959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"人流多係因為添好運咋 唔係你個租位呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26257b3c979aae6e611651b04bae0980ae735cc6","tid":82483,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>業主幾時先明白，人地生意做得住你個租金回報先穩定，其實係坐埋同一條船，成日都唔想個租客有飯開，要自己賺晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢以為走一個可以搵到另一個租<br />\n以前啲旺區就係既，爭住租<br />\n而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢個位咁撚西，唔係添好運有米芝蓮星，都唔會有人去<br />\nOn9業主就以為自己間舗係靚舖</blockquote><br />\n佢九成諗住屈鳩添好運架啫<br />\n點知人地一早開晒分店啦，洗鳩攬住間舖<br />\nbtw, 特登買間舖黎加租真係賤到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2774e776607f4f99eba80fce3d58caa5ac1917f7","tid":82483,"uid":18547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你阿"},{"pid":"862aa5a0bec0f02158fcfb31f4732107d552abf9","tid":82483,"uid":648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ab3b9a514f8a0167e2f55eb8e0edaf82e7b988","tid":82483,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08573be0aa2fe2fad3b41673f3d2a0d273b7a58","tid":82483,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:14:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我識個行家租左間舖十幾年，前年真係好差頂唔住問個業主可唔可以減租，個業主話唔得，所以佢就話唔續。<br />\n個業主之後周圍揾人接都無人理，就死死地氣揾返我個行家話平d續租，個行家疊埋心水唔做睬佢都有味，個舖一路吉到而家，差唔多三年。<br />\nd 陷家產業主有時真係抵撚死，二三線舖以為自己一線可以任叫價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我樓下都係，逼走左涼茶同漫畫鋪<br />\n吉左兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cbd65ead3416e80c43cb7989347dcf5de42382","tid":82483,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:14:09.000Z","msg":"大快人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b60cf81c44675b94204937a6d20e4505bf8caa","tid":82483,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"一千零一單炒家仆街大快人心個案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39